[[Platform Cooperativism 2016]] presentation via https://livestream.com/internetsociety/platformcoop2016/videos/141869834

==Description==

Report 1 - Berlin

"(15 mins) Thomas Dönnebrink - After the PlatformCoop event in November 2015 at The New School, PlatformCoopBerlin carried the coming out party of the cooperative Internet to Europe. Here, it ignited additional torches. In his presentation, Dönnebrink will focus on the outcomes of the activities of the PlatformCoopBerlin group, which included more than 10 events in Europe and Mexico, which did not only further disseminate the concept of platform cooperativism but also helped to bring a European and Latin American focus to this political and economical debate and practice."

